  "title": "✈️ (Travel Opportunities!!) ✈️ Events Management Trainee",
  "description": "<p>🎉 Events Management Trainee! 🎉</p><p>Love vibes, people, and making things happen? We’re on the hunt for energetic go-getters to help us pull off epic events, roadshows, and activations across Singapore!</p><p></p><p>What You’ll Be Up To:</p><p>✨ Planning and running exciting roadshows</p><p>✨ Boosting awareness and driving sales on-site</p><p>✨ Turning events into fun, memorable experiences</p><p></p><p>Who We’re Looking For:</p><p>💬 Great communicator & team player</p><p>🗂 Organized multitasker who can handle the chaos</p><p>⚡️ Proactive, energetic, and ready to dive in</p><p>🎯 Experience in events, marketing, or customer-facing roles? Bonus points – but not a must</p><p></p><p>Why You’ll Love It Here:</p><p>🎈 Fun, lively, and supportive team</p><p>🚀 Learn tons and grow fast</p><p>🎉 Work on exciting, high-energy projects</p><p></p><p>Perks & Extras:</p><p>💡 Real hands-on events experience</p><p>🤝 Meet awesome brands and clients</p><p>📈 Career growth opportunities</p>",
